ity of streamers at different pressures is confirmed\nin all gases; the minimal diameters are smaller than in earlier measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2009 17:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2010 16:40:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-03-24"}
