ing our numerical\nestimate of the true separability function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2009 19:43:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2010 17:11:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
